{"id": 2766, "genre": 1000, "title": "你觉得哪些春节广告里的常见情节，现在可以稍微换一换了？", "description": "总有一种“年年到这个时候，广告就长得差不多”的感觉。（题图来自：iStock ©️ roberuto）", "record_count": 19329, "comment_count": 24, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190129172731zsZO6b4ESAyTcPrt.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-02-10T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5321, "title": "你觉得哪些春节广告里的常见情节，现在可以稍微换一换了？", "content": "你觉得哪些春节广告常见情节，其实可以稍稍更新一下了？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 325748, "content": "“过年回家”默认一定是从大城市回到遥远的乡下", "image": "img/option/option/20190201165249KSgDIRqh5iJZBAsr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 325749, "content": "爸妈和儿女一定会在电话里闹点小矛盾", "image": "img/option/option/20190201165342A9dGZpHaR1LcXVrm.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 325750, "content": "总是会有“儿女说不回家，爸妈失落地挂上电话”的情节", "image": "img/option/option/20190201165356E1tQMTjOwkF4uh2V.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 325752, "content": "通常会用“妈妈忙着做饭，爸爸负责训话”表现父母分工", "image": "img/option/option/20190201165442dUEickyuYbvzVB2m.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 325753, "content": "家庭小矛盾最后总是以“一起吃年夜饭+敬酒”解决", "image": "img/option/option/201902011657563STma9HJyhqul8RC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 325760, "content": "吃年夜饭的时候全家人都会穿大红色唐装", "image": "img/option/option/20190201165454au3IC72SrNL1iFhW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 325761, "content": "儿女进门的时候，屋外通常会配上飘雪+一盏路灯", "image": "img/option/option/20190201165506VOSq0zsxMCfmGd4k.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 325762, "content": "表现“思乡之情”，一定会拍从飞驰的火车车窗向外看的侧脸", "image": "img/option/option/20190201165546BoEn3lpKwdC6tGAF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}